      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in roadworthy shape. It requires major mechanical work, as the engine is experiencing significant oil leaks and the transmission struggles to engage properly. The body also shows heavy wear, including noticeable rust patches and a cracked windshield. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or a donor car for parts.",
